videos.description: Michigan's Derrick Walton Jr gets the steal and goes coast to coast for the layup.
videos.headline: Michigan's Walton causing havoc on both ends.

videos.description: Swanigan swats the layup, Purdue recovers and then he sets up down low for the easy hook shot.
videos.headline: Caleb Swanigan doing it all.

videos.description: D.J Wilson keeps up his torrid shooting in the 1st half
videos.headline: D.J Wilson from outside

videos.description: P.J. Thompson capped an entertaining first half vs. Michigan with a half-court shot.
videos.headline: Purdue beats halftime horn with halfcourt heave

videos.description: The Head Coach breaks down his team's 1st half performance with ESPN's Molly McGrath.
videos.headline: Michigan Head Coach John Beilein breaks down the Wolverines performance in the 1st Half.

videos.description: Purdue's Carsen Edwards, grabs the rebound and goes coast to coast and finishes with a crafty Euro-step to put Purdue up 2 with under 30 seconds left in regulation.
videos.headline: Edwards goes coast to coast

videos.description: Derek Irvin ties the game for the Wolverines with a late layup.
videos.headline: Irvin's game tying layup to send Michigan Purdue to OT
